name: Consistent Care Services- COVID Vaccine Site
notes: ***Joints for Jabs for any state resident in conjunction with Top Shelf Cannabis. This is a clinic for 1st or 2nd doses of the Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine or the single dose of the Johnson & Johnson vaccine*** This clinic is located at Top Shelf Cannabis at 1305 S. Hayford Rd.  ***With your vaccination you will receive one free pre-rolled joint grown locally by With It Weed.  You may choose either Indica-God's Gift or Sativa-Mimosa  with your vaccination AND in addition 20% off your purchase on July 8th during that visit. ***Residents of ANY state are now eligible for the vaccine, but you still must have photo ID and be 21 or over to enter the building*** *VERY IMPORTANT* ***Please complete all the insurance/Medicare/Medicaid information when registering online for your appointment to avoid filling it out at the clinic**
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
